[[!meta title="Published puppet modules: Collectd, Java, Prayer and ns_webmail_proxy"]]

[Steven and I](https://sans.ethz.ch) are continuing to clean up 
our puppet repo, which resulted in four new
(more or less standalone) puppet modules:

 * [collectd](http://git.sans.ethz.ch/?p=puppet-modules/collectd;a=summary): Create monitoring and monitored hosts with puppet
 * [java](http://git.sans.ethz.ch/?p=puppet-modules/java;a=summary): Include all java stuff you ever dreamed of
 * [prayer](http://git.sans.ethz.ch/?p=puppet-modules/prayer;a=summary): A lightweight webmail
 * [ns_webmail_proxy](http://git.sans.ethz.ch/?p=puppet-modules/prayer;a=summary): Using prayer and postfix to create a webmail proxy that can also send e-mails

If you enjoy them, we would be happy if you drop us a mail ;-)

